{"tid":1582317,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"回應國際特赦調查 警方稱一向尊重被羈留人士權利","createTime":"2019-09-20T04:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T04:27:31.000Z","uid":56881,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2ab531e9758da10a19b110c57eb876a6dba8aa","tid":1582317,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:04:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%89%B9%E8%B5%A6%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1-%E5%90%91%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E8%A2%AB%E7%BE%88%E7%95%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9-003322589.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%2589%25B9%25E8%25B5%25A6%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25B0%258A%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%25BE%2588%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2588%25A9-003322589.html&d=56TVgGSmQeZ0yTrvrOoz8iMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=82f34b62\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%89%B9%E8%B5%A6%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1-%E5%90%91%E5%B0%8A%E9%87%8D%E8%A2%AB%E7%BE%88%E7%95%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9-003322589.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sobcsrVwIPIRZnJz1j8FmA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-09/9883e520-db53-11e9-8ff0-0ee0e5e44b7a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FsobcsrVwIPIRZnJz1j8FmA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2F9883e520-db53-11e9-8ff0-0ee0e5e44b7a&h=b79277ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回應國際特赦調查 警方稱一向尊重被羈留人士權利 (Getty Images)<br />\n<br />\n警方回應國際特赦組織調查時表示，一向尊重被羈留人士的尊嚴、私隱和權利，不評論個別事件，如果被羈留人士有任何不滿，可根據現行機制投訴。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，任何情況下，如果被羈留人士要求接受治療，值日官會將該人送往政府醫院或診所，在沒有對調查過程或司法程序造成不合理延誤和妨礙下，被羈留人士會獲安排與外界溝通，例如尋求法律援助等。警方又說，警員使用武力有嚴格指引，所使用的必定是為完成合法任務而須使用的最低武力，警員會時刻保持高度克制。<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織訪問超過20名被捕人士，並收集律師與醫護人員的證詞。組織批評，香港6月大規模示威開始以來，警隊任意拘捕，扣留期間毒打和酷刑對待被捕人士，日益嚴重，形容警隊做法令人震驚，有明顯報復心態，以魯莽與非法手段對付在示威現場的人士，要求當局迅速進行獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n權利係咪包括比黑警毒打?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dcda4da7ab47a9ee06208f5ffced2995322766","tid":1582317,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:24:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果被羈留人士有任何不滿，可根據現行機制投訴 </span></span><br />\n其實佢講咩都唔重要。因為唔會有人信 佢認既話仲驚。"},{"pid":"40e5418404a2457b6258b2662e1121fc92a741b9","tid":1582317,"uid":231909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"遇到挑釁打人記得大嗌<br />\n「以武制暴」、「止暴制亂」、「跟機打波」、「Defend ourselves」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WSsXUdU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSsXUdU.jpg&h=71e58159&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f9299b55b39f6a15e25ba39cec3288860057c7e","tid":1582317,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"言行不一既代表"},{"pid":"3aa8bd250e53eb71980af169ceeeb09c0860a94d","tid":1582317,"uid":7468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"警員會時刻保持高度克制<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc8fb66d044f298e25bb1622fc90b8da2b87083","tid":1582317,"uid":259813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"成鳩日講完就當係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己都呃唔到自己啦fa"}]}